[Introduction]
	In real life you need to tidy up things like your clothes and your house when your parents are going to visit you (true story).
When you're in front of the computer / laptop / netbook screen download things like images, videos, audio files and documents.
When you go to your "Download" folder and there is a total chaos then you realize that you should tidy these things to clean up this mess
and to tell the truth, is one of the most boring things. You lose much of your precious time and this is where tidyman coming!

[About Tidyman]
	Tidyman is a tool that automatically tidies your images, your videos, your audio files and your documents . It is very easy to use and you need only few seconds to run it!! 
	It creates a folder named "tidyman" in the folder you want to tidy and it creates folders 
based on what type of file you want to tidy.

[Author]
	Pavlos Ratis ( dastergon )
	dastergon [at] gmail [dot] com
	http://dastergon.gr

[Usage]
  ./tidyman.sh [OPTION] [PATH]
Options:
-a - Tidy only audio
-d - Tidy only documents
-h - Display this help and exit
-i - Tidy only images
-v - Tidy only videos

[Examples]
 
Single argument - tidy only images.
	user@linux~$./tidyman.sh -i Downloads/

Double argument - tidy images and videos
	user@linux~$./tidyman.sh -iv Downloads/

All arguments - tidy all (audio,documents,images,videos)
	user@linux~$./tidyman.sh -adiv Downloads/

 